'''南峇山'''（{{lang-ms|Gunung Lambak}}）位于[[马来西亚|马来西亚]][[柔佛州|柔佛州]][[居銮|居銮]]，座落在居銮市东侧约5公里处，主峰高度[[海拔|海拔]]510米。那里的森林保留地是当地的旅游景点。<ref name="Gunung Lambak">{{cite web|url=http://www.mpkluang.gov.my/web/guest/hutan-rekreasi-gunung-lambak|title=Gunung Lambak Recreational Park|publisher=Kluang Municipal Council|accessdate=6 Oct 2014|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141008220814/http://www.mpkluang.gov.my/web/guest/hutan-rekreasi-gunung-lambak|archivedate=2014-10-08}}</ref><ref name="JohortourismView43">{{cite web|url=http://www.johortourism.com.my/destination/view.cfm?ID=A7AC586B-F946-447D-A29BA35284FCE3B5|title=Mount Lambak Recreational Forest|author=Virtual Malaysia|publisher=Tourism Johor Official Portal|accessdate=17 Sep 2012|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://archive.is/20130221080205/http://www.johortourism.com.my/destination/view.cfm?ID=A7AC586B-F946-447D-A29BA35284FCE3B5|archivedate=2013-02-21}}</ref>
